🔥 正確解法（完整SQL）

Step 1：先定義 migration 對象（你已經有）

WITH PURE_1 AS (
    SELECT DISTINCT SK_CUST_ID
    FROM (
        SELECT SK_CUST_ID
        FROM BANCS_SK_CUST_INFO
        WHERE CUST_RE_NO_FLG = '1'
        EXCEPT
        SELECT SK_CUST_ID
        FROM BANCS_SK_CUST_INFO
        WHERE CUST_RE_NO_FLG IN ('2','3')
    ) t
)

⸻

Step 2：抓 PB 現況

, PB_NOW AS (
    SELECT DISTINCT cif_key, cust_nme
    FROM PB_CUSTOMER_FACT
)

⸻

Step 3：找「pure1 有進 PB 的」

, JOIN_RESULT AS (
    SELECT 
        c.CustomerNo,
        d.cif_key,
        c.cust_nme AS buffer_name,
        p.cust_nme AS pb_name
    FROM PURE_1 t
    JOIN Customer_Migrate_buffer c
        ON c.CustomerNo = t.SK_CUST_ID
    JOIN BSA_SUB_CUST_FACT d
        ON d.CustomerNo = c.CustomerNo
    JOIN PB_NOW p
        ON p.cif_key = d.cif_key
)

⸻

Step 4：關鍵 👉 判斷「是不是原本就存在 PB」

👉 你需要一個「migration before snapshot」

但你現在沒有 historical table，所以只能用 proxy：

⚠️ proxy 判斷法（實務常用）

SELECT *
FROM JOIN_RESULT
WHERE ISNULL(buffer_name,'#') = ISNULL(pb_name,'#');

👉 你那 36 筆就是這裡來的

